1.21 2010-12-06
 - Restored missing POT/PO translation sources (Damyan Ivanov, AZAWAWI)
 - rename method 'spell_preferences' to 'plugin_preferences', so that the
   dialogue can also be called from the plugin manager (ZENOG)
